<h2>Instructions For Completion</h2>
<br />
<br />
<p>The aim of this survey is to find out about your health and how it impacts on activities of
daily life. The answers you give in the survey will be treated in the <b>strictest confidence</b>.</p>
<p><b>Please answer even if you have no problems with your health.</b></p>
<p>Please answer all of the questions unless the instructions ask you to do something else.</p>
<p><b>When you have finished please check that you have answered all of the questions
and then press submit. Please submit the completed survey within the next two weeks.</b></p>
<p>More details about this project are available in the @Html.ActionLink("Patient Information Sheet.", "DownloadFile", "Home", null, null)</p>
<p>If you would like further information about this project, please contact the North
Staffordshire Health Survey co-ordinator on 01782 733905.</p>
<br />
<br />
<p class="text-center"><b>Thank you for your help with this research project</b></p>
